metadata.name: Broken and Healed
metadata.description:
"I was once broken."
"Heart."
"Body."
"and Soul."
"But, now I know, I have to get up."
"Learn from my mistakes."
"Set a new vision."
"Vision to see goodness in every single thing."
"Even in my pain, there is always goodness."
"It teaches me something."
"Kindness always mend the wounded."
"I was once broken, but now I'm healed."

Artist: Soritoea
Tools: Adobe Photoshop, Wacom Tablet
Dimension: 2800 x 3000 px , 300 dpi
Year: 2023
